  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5446092">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5446092/" class="title-link">半推半就的“金钱关系”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5446092"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fenglong88/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1040358-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fenglong88/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">fenglong88</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-05-29"
      class="main-meta">2012-05-29 13:01:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5446092_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在日常生活中，当我们说：谁与谁有“金钱关系”时，语义之中往往指向不“道德”的内容或应单纯经济上的关联。当我们把“谁与谁”中的“谁”的替换成“国家”时，我们就会发现，其实我们对真正的“金钱关系”的了解是少之又少的。  在中国的历史上，历来有一种轻视商业和商人的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5446092_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5446092_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










